WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.965 --> 00:00:17.005
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:22.926 --> 00:00:28.005
What are you going to make?
Potlakaya Stuffed Curry (Snake Gourd Stuffed Curry)

00:00:33.543 --> 00:00:37.157
Ingredients required to make Potlakaya Stuffed Curry

00:00:37.369 --> 00:00:46.879
Snake Gourd, Onions, Sesame Powder, Coconut Powder, Garam Masala, Ginger-Garlic Paste

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:57.787
Seasoning Seeds, Curry Leaves, Coriander,
Lemon, Salt, Turmeric, Red Chilli Powder, Oil

00:01:01.351 --> 00:01:06.631
Take a pan and heat some oil

00:01:09.941 --> 00:01:14.881
Fry a bowl of chopped onions

00:01:18.718 --> 00:01:22.116
Fry til the onions are brown in color

00:01:30.569 --> 00:01:33.133
Take the fried onions aside

00:01:40.410 --> 00:01:44.947
Roast the sesame seeds and then
grind them into a powder and add the fried onions

00:01:49.521 --> 00:01:53.690
Add 4 tsp of red chilli powder
to the sesame powder &amp; fried onions

00:01:55.851 --> 00:02:00.133
Add 2 tsp of dry coconut powder

00:02:01.471 --> 00:02:07.323
Add 2 tsp of garam masala
and some salt as required

00:02:08.750 --> 00:02:13.828
Add 1 tsp of ginger-garlic paste

00:02:16.943 --> 00:02:20.589
Add a pinch of turmeric

00:02:30.789 --> 00:02:36.178
Mix well by adding some water
(only as required to make the stuffing)

00:03:03.941 --> 00:03:10.087
Cut the snake gourd into pieces and
stuff them with the prepared stuffing

00:03:15.212 --> 00:03:20.028
Take a pan and heat some oil

00:03:20.203 --> 00:03:24.957
Add some mustard &amp; cumin seeds

00:03:27.617 --> 00:03:30.593
Add some curry leaves

00:03:33.444 --> 00:03:37.758
Add a pinch of turmeric

00:03:41.327 --> 00:03:49.003
Now start frying the stuffed snake gourd pieces

00:04:00.533 --> 00:04:05.517
Close the lid and cook for 3-5 mins

00:04:20.212 --> 00:04:25.773
Add some water to the remaining of the
prepared stuffing and make a gravy

00:04:25.987 --> 00:04:31.240
Add the gravy into the pan

00:04:38.386 --> 00:04:42.531
Close the lid and cook for 2 mins

00:04:50.107 --> 00:04:54.877
Add some coriander

00:04:59.826 --> 00:05:05.419
Add very little lemon squeeze

00:05:06.905 --> 00:05:15.320
Mix well and take it into a serving bowl

